Camping tents come in various product types, including dome tents, tunnel tents, geodesic tents, A-frame tents, and other specialized designs. These variations cater to different camping needs, from backpacking to family camping trips. Capacity is another key segment, with tents available for 1-2 persons, 3-4 persons, 5-6 persons, and larger groups of 7-8 persons or more. This segmentation ensures that consumers can find tents tailored to their specific group sizes. In terms of distribution channels, the market is divided between online and offline retail, providing consumers with multiple options to purchase camping tents according to their preferences.

